Package: periodic-table
Version: 1.0.4
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, libsdl2-2.0-0, libsdl2-image-2.0-0, libsdl2-mixer-2.0-0, libsdl2-ttf-2.0-0
Maintainer: Gaurav Kushwaha <gaurav.kush1225@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Gaurav-Kushwaha-1225/Periodic_Table
Description: Interactive periodic table application
 A Kivy-based periodic table application displaying detailed properties
 of chemical elements using the framework approved by the International
 Union of Pure and Applied Chemistry (IUPAC).
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive periodic table display with all 118 elements
  - Detailed element properties (electron configuration, atomic weight, etc.)
  - Search functionality by name, atomic number, electronegativity, etc.
  - High-resolution element images
  - Educational content and chemistry dictionary
  - Clean, modern interface built with KivyMD
 .
 Perfect for students, educators, and chemistry enthusiasts.
